":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" for Jerusalem and Zion. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 20:5","book":"Exo","chapter":20,"verse":5},{"label":"Ex 34:14","book":"Exo","chapter":34,"verse":14},{"label":"Dt 4:24","book":"Deu","chapter":4,"verse":24},{"label":"Dt 5:9","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":9},{"label":"Dt 6:15","book":"Deu","chapter":6,"verse":15},{"label":"Jos 24:19","book":"Jos","chapter":24,"verse":19},{"label":"Nah 1:2","book":"Nam","chapter":1,"verse":2},{"label":"Zch 8:2","book":"Zec","chapter":8,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Zec:1:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I am fiercely angry with the nations that are at ease, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 34:2","book":"Isa","chapter":34,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nah 1:2","book":"Nam","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" for I was a little angry, but they made the destruction worse. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit they helped for evil"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 34:2","book":"Isa","chapter":34,"verse":2},{"label":"Nah 1:2","book":"Nam","chapter":1,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit they helped for evil"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Zec:1:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, this is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says: In mercy, I have returned to Jerusalem; my house will be rebuilt within it —this is the declaration of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies —and a measuring line will be stretched out over Jerusalem. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 21:13","book":"2Ki","chapter":21,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 28:17","book":"Isa","chapter":28,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 34:11","book":"Isa","chapter":34,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lm 2:8","book":"Lam","chapter":2,"verse":8,"letter":"d"